I had a facial in the Spa that was the best I've ever had, and a fabulous massage.	The suite was large, although with a slightly awkward layout, and the ensuite had a large spa bath with a large hatch through to the bedroom so that someone in the bath could watch the bedroom TV or converse with their partner in the bedroom.	I did not get to try the spa which I regret and the gym room is a bit small but it does have all the usual required equipment.	The only disappointment was the size of the spa which had few facilities besides some treatment rooms, but the treatments and technicians were SUPERB!